    "created_at": "2015-12-08T09:29:40Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-08T09:29:40Z",
    "body": "V8 4.7 is compatible with V8 4.5's APIs, so we don't need to update a bunch of modules this time.\n\nUsing Node with an unmatched V8 version is usually a bad idea, since Node might rely on certain V8 version's behaviors.\n"
