    "created_at": "2015-12-08T09:40:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-12-08T09:40:58Z",
    "body": "OK, so this upgrade was necessary in order to bump Chromium to v47?\n\nWhen we bump Electron in Atom we will have to resolve issues with npm v3 though; it's not playing nice right now (unless someone has resolved the issues in the last few weeks). Hopefully not too big of a hurdle. But my comment regarding Node LTS was specifically related to stability concerns.\n"
