    "updated_at": "2015-12-08T11:53:52Z",
    "body": "> OK, so this upgrade was necessary in order to bump Chromium to v47?\n\nYeah.\n\nThe stability of Node LTS is largely depending on using an old but stable V8 version, so every time we bump the Chrome version, we break the stability a bit.\n"
